{"tid":2044924,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[完美反駁藍絲] 突然明白美國警察同香港警察有咩唔同","createTime":"2020-05-31T12:09:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T12:10:43.000Z","uid":340729,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b63cfbc2e02f14505c7388fcaf742fc5dde66230","tid":2044924,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T12:09:53.000Z","msg":"單睇表面 <span style=\"color: red;\">兩者都係有部分警察使用暴力</span> 形成警暴<br />\n<br />\n但其實個問題<span style=\"color: red;\">不在於暴力與否</span><br />\n而係<span style=\"color: red;\">事後的態度問題</span><br />\n<br />\n香港警察打人 上司包庇 一開始只是<span style=\"color: red;\">簡單地訓斥</span> <span style=\"color: green;\">毫無威嚇</span><br />\n甚至是立惡法如<span style=\"color: red;\">禁警員編號</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">禁公開姓名</span> <span style=\"color: green;\">助長歪風</span><br />\n去到近日 甚至警察<span style=\"color: red;\">持刀執法</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">後數偷水</span> 通通也是<span style=\"color: green;\">刑事罪行</span> 卻沒有人出來阻止 甚至掩飾<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而美國警察使用的暴力完全與香港警察相似</span> 這是從影片中看到的<br />\n但事後卻是會<span style=\"color: gold;\">認錯</span> 會<span style=\"color: gold;\">下跪</span> 或許我都知道係<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">公關show</span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">但與香港比較<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港警察連認錯的勇氣都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div>"},{"pid":"34baee19ad6c9b267f19777b1523264f18b5ebf6","tid":2044924,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T12:10:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r1XYuTb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr1XYuTb.png&h=6d59c9b7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}